text: Shockaloo Creek is a stream in the U.S. state of Mississippi. Shockaloo is a name derived from the Choctaw language meaning "cypress tree". Variant names are "Schock Creek" and "Shockaloe Creek". ==References== Category:Rivers of Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Leake County, Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Scott County, Mississippi
title: Shockaloo Creek
